# AutoDQ Analytics

AutoDQ Analytics is an automated data quality and analytics framework.

It helps users:
- Load datasets
- Profile data
- Diagnose data quality issues
- Recommend cleaning steps
- Generate visuals
- Run simple `.adql` analytics scripts
- Export reports

## Current Stage

Stage 1: Core Python package foundation.
